OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMany places will have a dry day
OL,6,Falthough the odd shower possible
OL,7,Facross the far west. Some bright or
OL,8,Fsunny spells breaking through at
OL,9,Ftimes, more especially along the north
OL,10,Fcoast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening,
OL,13,Falthough some rain in the west later.
OL,14,FThen outbreaks of rain will spread to
OL,15,Fmost places during the early hours. A
OL,16,Fmild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
