OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA cloudy day with some
OL,6,Foccasional rain or drizzle, perhaps
OL,7,Fturning more persistent for a time in
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Drier and clearer with
OL,9,Fa few showers by evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FUnsettled with showers or longer
OL,13,Fspells of rain on Thursday. Brighter
OL,14,Fwith a few showers on Friday. Further
OL,15,Frain spreading east on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
